ormal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"id\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;letter-spacing:-.15pt\">Inovasi</span><span lang=\"id\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;letter-spacing:.4pt\">\n</span><span lang=\"id\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;\nletter-spacing:-.15pt\">pembelajaran</span><span lang=\"id\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\nmso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoBodyText\" style=\"margin-top:6.45pt;margin-right:6.15pt;margin-bottom:\n0cm;margin-left:43.65pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\n151%\"><span lang=\"id\">Guru<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>perlu<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>memiliki<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\">\n</span>keinginan<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>untuk<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>mengubah,<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\">\n</span>mengembangkan<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span>dan<span style=\"letter-spacing:.05pt\"> </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.15pt\">meningkatkan\ncara mengajarnya agar mampu menghasilkan </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:\n-.1pt\">pembelajaran yang</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-.05pt\"> </span>sesuai<span style=\"letter-spacing:.95pt\"> </span>dengan<span style=\"letter-spacing:1.3pt\"> </span>kebutuhan<span style=\"letter-spacing:2.7pt\"> </span>kelasnya.</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:43.65pt;text-indent:-14.25pt;\nline-height:13.2pt;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo1;\ntab-stops:43.65pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"id\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\nletter-spacing:-.1pt\">b.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;