(552,	95,	'F. METODE PENELITIAN',	'<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28.35pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -28.35pt; color: inherit;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><b>A.&nbsp;</b></font></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 7pt; font-weight: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span><span dir=\"LTR\" style=\"text-indent: -28.35pt; color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"></span><b style=\"text-indent: -28.35pt; color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Lokasi dan waktu</span></b><br></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:21.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:28.35pt;line-height:200%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Penelitian\nini dilaksanakan di SMA Islam Sultan Agung 1 Semarang di bawah Yayasan Badan\nWakaf Sultan Agung Semarang.Yayasan ini semula bernama Yayasan Badan Wakaf yang\ndidirikan oleh sekelompok cendekiawan muslim Jawa Tengah (Semarang) yang sadar\ndan menaruh perhatian terhadap perkembangan dan keadaan umat Islam dan bangsa\nIndonesia pada umumnya sejak awal proklamasi kemerdekaan RI. Status sebagai\nbadan wakaf diperoleh secara resmi pada tanggal 13 Juli 1950 dengan Akta\nNotaris Tan A Sioe Nomor 86 dengan pengurus pertama sebagai berikut. ( Sumber :\nDokumen SMA Islam Sultan Agung 1 Semarang tahun 2016)&nbsp; :<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:21.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Pelindung&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; :&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Residen Malino<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:21.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ketua&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; :&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Dr. Abdul Gaffar Sd.M<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:21.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Wakil Ketua&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; :&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ustadz Abu Bakar Assegaf<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:21.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Penulis I&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; :&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; R. Soeryadi<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:21.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Penulis II&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; :&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ali Al Idrus<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:21.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\nline-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Komisaris-Komisaris&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; :&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Moh. Toyib Tohari<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:148.85pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\nauto;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Zaenal\nAmien<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:148.85pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\nauto;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Abdul\nKadir Al Idrus<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:148.85pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:\nauto;line-height:200%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Wartono<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:21.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:28.35pt;line-height:200%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Seiring\ndengan perkembangan zaman, dan sesuai peraturan dari kementerian hukum dan ham\nsetiap lembaga yang berbadan hukum secara periodik harus di daftarkan ulang.\nOleh sebab itu yayasan badan wakaf&nbsp; ini\nmengalami beberapa kali perubahan. Sedangkan yang terakhir dengan Akta Notaris\nRM. Soetomo No. 8 tanggal 13 Oktober 1980.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:21.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:28.35pt;line-height:200%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Dalam\nakta tersebut diantaranya menyebutkan bahwa Yayasan Badan Wakaf Sultan Agung\nberlandaskan Pancasila dan bertujuan menyebarkan pendidikan dan ajaran Islam\nyang dijiwai oleh dakwah Islamiah.Untuk mencapai tujuan tersebut diantaranya\ndengan usaha-usaha mendirikan lembaga-lembaga pendidikan mulai Taman\nKanak-Kanak, Sekolah Dasar, Sekolah Lanjutan, sampai Perguruan Tinggi dan\npesantren serta lembaga lainnya guna menyebarkan syiar Islam.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:21.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:28.35pt;line-height:200%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Pada\ntanggal 2 Januari 1966 SMA Sultan Agung 1 Semarang didirikan dengan lokasi\ngedung di Jalan Suramenggalan 62. Pada tahun 1968 pindah ke jalan Seroja untuk\nbeberapa bulan saja dan akhirnya pindah ke jalan Mataram 657 Semarang hingga\nsekarang. Pada tanggal 1 Juni 1970 SMA Sultan Agung 1 memperoleh status\nterdaftar. Beracuan dari perolehan status terdaftar inilah sebagai tanda\nberdirinya SMA Sultan Agung 1 Semarang yang seterusnya diperingati sebagai\n\"Milad SMA ISSA 1\" setiap tahun.( Sumber : Dokumen SMA Islam Sultan\nAgung 1 Semarang tahun 2016).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:21.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:28.35pt;line-height:200%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Pada\nawalnya gedung yang berada di Jalan Mataram hanya satu unit gedung. Kemudian\nsecara berangsur-angsur gedung diperbaharui dan ditambah hingga sekarang SMA\nIslam Sulan Agung 1 Semarang memiliki tiga lantai dan menjadi empat unit serta\nsatu unit kantin yang representatif.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:21.3pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:28.35pt;line-height:200%\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Sejak\nawal berdirinya hingga tahun pelajaran 2016/2017, SMA Islam Sultan Agung 1\nSemarang telah dipimpin tujuh kepala sekolah, yaitu:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:42.55pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-indent:-21.25pt;line-height:200%;mso-list:l11 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span style=\"font-size:\n12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Bapak Drs.\nIswoyo PIA&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ( 1966 - 1970 )<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:42.55pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-indent:-21.25pt;line-height:200%;mso-list:l11 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span style=\"font-size:\n12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ibu Hj.\nHudahaniem, B.Sc.&nbsp; ( 1970 - 1997 )<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:42.55pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-indent:-21.25pt;line-height:200%;mso-list:l11 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span style=\"font-size:\n12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Bapak Drs. Dadi\nBasuki&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ( 1997 - 2002 )<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:42.55pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-indent:-21.25pt;line-height:200%;mso-list:l11 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span style=\"font-size:\n12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Bapak Drs. Risno\nSetiyono&nbsp; ( 2002 - 2006 )<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:42.55pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-indent:-21.25pt;line-height:200%;mso-list:l11 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span style=\"font-size:\n12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Bapak. Much.\nMuchlis Hidayatullah, S.Pd&nbsp; (2006 - 2010)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:42.55pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-indent:-21.25pt;line-height:200%;mso-list:l11 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span style=\"font-size:\n12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Bapak</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">Drs. Sarjana, M.Si</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\nline-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\"> ( 2010 – 2015 )<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:42.55pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-add-space:auto;\ntext-indent:-21.25pt;line-height:200%;mso-list:l11 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">7.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><span style=\"font-size:\n12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Ibu Dra. Siti\nMubarokatut Darojati ( 2015 – Sekarang )</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28.35pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Metode\npenelitian adalah rangkaian dari cara / kegiatan pelaksanaan penelitian dan\ndidasari oleh pandangan filosofis, asumsi dasar, dan ideologis serta pertanyaan\ndan isu yang dihadapi. Sebuah penelitian memiliki rancangan penelitian\ntertentu. Rancangan ini menjelaskan prosedur / langkah-langkah yang harus\ndijalani, waktu penelitian, kondisi data dikumpulkan, sumber data serta dengan\ncara apa data tersebut dibuat dan diolah. Tujuan dari rancangan ini adalah\nmenggunakan metode penelitian yang baik dan tepat, dirancang kegiatan yang bisa\nmemberikan jawaban yang benar terhadap pertanyaan-pertanyaan dalam penelitian.\n(Sudjana, 2006:21)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28.35pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Penelitian yang&nbsp;\ndilaksanakan&nbsp; di&nbsp; lapangan&nbsp;\nadalah&nbsp; meneliti&nbsp; masalah&nbsp;\nyang&nbsp; sifatnya kualitatif, yakni\nprosedur data penelitian yang menghasilkan data deskriptif berupa&nbsp; kata-kata tertulis&nbsp; atau&nbsp;\nlisan&nbsp; dari&nbsp; orang-orang&nbsp;\ndan&nbsp; perilaku&nbsp; yang diamati. Sehingga dapat dikatakan bahwa\npenelitian ini bersifat deskriptif kualitatif artinya penulis&nbsp; menganalisis&nbsp;\ndan&nbsp; menggambarkan&nbsp; penelitian secara objektif dan detail untuk\nmendapatkan hasil yang akurat.<span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">(Sudjana, 2006 : 25). <o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28.35pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Jenis\npenilitian ini adalah penelitian lapangan ((<i>field reseach)</i> yaitu suatu\npenelitian yang dilakukan di kancah atau di medan terjadi gejala-gejala.(</span><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">.(John\nW Best, 1982:98)<span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">).</span>\nJenis Penelitian lapangan (<i>field research</i>) yaitu dengan mengadakan\npenelitian terhadap objek yang dituju untuk memperoleh data yang benar dan\nterpercaya tentang penggunaan metodehiwar dalam pembelajaran keterampilan\nberbicarapada mata pelajaran bahasa Arabdi SMA Islam Sultan Agung Semarang<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 28.35pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: -28.35pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:200%;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">3.1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></b><!--[endif]--><span dir=\"LTR\"></span><b><span lang=\"IN\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Subyek Penelitian<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28.35pt; line-height: 200%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial